Here's the `getControlPoints` method for the `NurbsSurface` class:

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor(controlPoints, weights, knotsU, knotsV) {
        this.controlPoints = controlPoints;
        this.weights = weights;
        this.knotsU = knotsU;
        this.knotsV = knotsV;
    }

    getControlPoints() {
        return [...this.controlPoints]; // Return a copy of the control points array
    }
}
```

This method returns a copy of the `controlPoints` array, allowing for safe read-only access to the control points without modifying the original array.
